WEBVTT

00:00.080 --> 00:01.120
Now in the army

00:02.360 --> 00:03.680
Most are our trusted men

00:03.920 --> 00:05.200
Chen Ying wants to kill me

00:05.920 --> 00:06.960
It's not that easy

00:07.440 --> 00:08.600
Now Prince Ning has controlled

00:08.600 --> 00:09.640
The court situation

00:10.600 --> 00:11.640
Has all the advantages

00:12.480 --> 00:13.800
If I raise troops now

00:14.640 --> 00:15.480
It's disloyalty

00:16.320 --> 00:17.640
Using the northern expedition to march south

00:18.160 --> 00:18.960
It's unjust

00:19.600 --> 00:20.960
Brothers fighting

00:22.160 --> 00:23.120
Is even unfilial

00:23.800 --> 00:24.920
An army without just cause

00:26.080 --> 00:27.320
How can it win?

00:27.560 --> 00:28.240
Your Highness

00:28.400 --> 00:29.840
Your Highness, Your Highness

00:31.680 --> 00:32.800
My mind is made up

00:33.360 --> 00:34.960
This matter, speak no more of it

00:40.440 --> 00:41.640
Since Lord Xie has come

00:42.160 --> 00:43.360
Stay with me in the army

00:44.000 --> 00:44.720
Zhu Yuanzhi

00:46.080 --> 00:47.120
Tomorrow you come with me

00:47.920 --> 00:48.960
To apologize with bared back
